'''Homogoni''' was an expensive [[Wood/Legends|wood]] used to make tables. Like all things, its cells were bound together by [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. In this wood's case, the cells were bound in long lines, which gave it its grain. During [[Jedi training/Legends|training]] session [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] successfully practiced [[Shatterpoint/Legends|shatterpoint]] technique, shattering the wood.

